@startuml
actor Admin
participant "API Client" as API
participant "UserController" as UC
participant "UserService" as US
participant "UserRepository" as UR

Admin -> API: Access user role management
API -> UC: GET /users
UC -> US: Retrieve users with roles
US -> UR: Query all users
UR --> US: Return user data
US --> UC: Return user list
UC --> API: Return user data
API -> Admin: Display user list

Admin -> API: Assign/Remove roles
API -> UC: POST/DELETE /users/{id}/roles
UC -> US: Validate and apply role changes
US -> UR: Update user roles
UR --> US: Confirm update
US --> UC: Return success/failure
UC --> API: Return operation result
API -> Admin: Display success/failure message
@enduml

